name: UMB Data Catalog
description: Search the UMB Data Catalog to discover datasets generated by UMB researchers and local expertise on publicly available and licensed datasets. Includes survey data on pharmacogenomics (PGx), health-related data from the Old Order Amish population, cardiovascular risk, diabetes, bone health, blood pressure, vascular imaging, aging, breast tissue density, platelet aggregation, microbiome, wellness, and brain imaging.
owner_name: University of Maryland, Baltimore - Health Sciences and Human Services Library
